Read data package report

Source: R/utilities.R
read_data_package_report_hymet.Rd

Read data package report

read_data_package_report_hymet(packageId, frmt = "xml", env = "production")

Arguments

packageId

(character) Data package identifier
frmt

(character) Format of the returned report. Can be: "xml", "html", or "char".
env

(character) Repository environment. Can be: "production", "staging", or "development".

Value

(xml_document) Data package report

Examples

# Read as XML
qualityReport <- read_data_package_report_hymet("knb-lter-knz.260.4")
qualityReport
